Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:15.22,0:00:18.15,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算翻过所有的杂志也没有用
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:18.51,0:00:22.11,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只能在这摇头叹息
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:23.39,0:00:26.50,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根本找不到 与我相称的衣服
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:26.64,0:00:30.54,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,世纪末的流行色
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:31.86,0:00:34.58,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全部都无法 讨得你的欢心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:34.78,0:00:38.38,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很抱歉让你失望了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:39.54,0:00:43.17,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如履薄冰这样不稳的步伐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:43.71,0:00:47.34,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,摇摇晃晃的又有什么不好呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:47.50,0:00:51.35,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使如此还是得向前迈进
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:51.74,0:00:56.02,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对我来说  一点也不成问题
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:00.97,0:01:05.07,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是与我紧紧地缠绕的话不行哟
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:05.16,0:01:08.87,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托你  别用那种冷冷的眼神望着我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:09.06,0:01:12.71,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让我照着自己的步调去做
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:13.07,0:01:16.90,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不然的话我很快就会崩溃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:17.41,0:01:20.90,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如履薄冰这样不稳的步伐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:21.44,0:01:24.88,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,摇摇晃晃的又有什么不好呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:25.33,0:01:29.41,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使如此还是得向前迈进
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:29.72,0:01:34.06,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对我来说  一点也不成问题
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:53.30,0:21:58.31,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Free Magic  真正的所在
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:58.80,0:22:03.98,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Free Magic  这就是爱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:04.19,0:22:09.37,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在冰冷的黑暗中  伸手寻找温暖
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:09.53,0:22:15.28,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总有一天  奇迹也一定会发生的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:17.87,0:22:28.21,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Free Magic 如果有爱 就绝对有具体的形式
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:28.72,0:22:39.22,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Free Magic 现在 在我手中 有诞生的气息
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:39.43,0:22:47.48,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使是精神饱满  也不能  太过勉强
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:47.85,0:22:52.78,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Free Magic  把些微的勇气
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:53.24,0:23:03.96,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Free Magic  凝聚起来  培育茁壮吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:01.29,0:00:02.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在瞬间明白所有真相
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:03.13,0:00:04.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要开始就不会停止
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:04.93,0:00:06.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天是不可思议的关键钥匙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:06.71,0:00:08.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,密室中的惊人手法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:08.76,0:00:10.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唯一看透真相的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:10.18,0:00:11.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是一个外表看似小孩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:11.12,0:00:12.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,智慧却过于常人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:12.25,0:00:14.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他就是 名侦探柯南
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:37.33,0:01:40.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我记得就在这附近了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:41.03,0:01:42.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是不是叫「光庄」啊？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:44.27,0:01:47.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是一栋就像要倒的房子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:50.62,0:01:52.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,该不会就是这里吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:53.49,0:01:55.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光居
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:57.52,0:01:59.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…不会吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:01.46,0:02:04.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,水中钥匙密室事件
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:08.20,0:02:08.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:09.31,0:02:12.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为今年春天这里就重新改建了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:13.82,0:02:16.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不知道有这么回事 害我吓了一跳呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:17.33,0:02:22.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和你读书的时候住的地方完全不一样吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:22.50,0:02:24.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然 天壤之别
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:24.78,0:02:28.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且是因为讨厌啰嗦的房东的我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:28.45,0:02:30.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,半年前就不租了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:31.31,0:02:32.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有这回事吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:36.52,0:02:37.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,婆婆
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:37.88,0:02:39.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你自己一个人住在这里吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:40.07,0:02:43.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 孩子们都到很远的地方去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:44.02,0:02:47.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过 现在有个孙子和我住在同楼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:48.29,0:02:49.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吃吧 吃吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:50.60,0:02:51.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好好吃的样子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:51.98,0:02:54.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样婆婆就不会无聊了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:55.43,0:02:56.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他叫做阿真
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:56.93,0:03:00.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在城南大学念建筑 不过…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:00.35,0:03:03.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最近常常把自己关在房里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:05.03,0:03:07.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,问他怎么回事 他也不肯讲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:07.82,0:03:10.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我在想身为名侦探的你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:10.18,0:03:12.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有可能问出什么原因
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:13.09,0:03:15.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以你才会打电话给我啊？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:15.65,0:03:19.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他说八点左右会来这里的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:20.28,0:03:21.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们过去看看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:22.95,0:03:25.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,四楼是我和孙子住的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:25.78,0:03:29.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一楼到三楼全部租给别人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:32.90,0:03:34.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奇怪了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:37.48,0:03:38.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也许睡着了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:38.76,0:03:40.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我用备用钥匙开门吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:41.20,0:03:42.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没关系吗？ 擅自开门
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:43.00,0:03:45.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无所谓 这是我孙子的房间
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:48.24,0:03:50.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿真 出去了吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:52.11,0:03:54.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是邋遢的孩子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:57.98,0:03:58.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这到底是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:03.32,0:04:04.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,借过一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:08.92,0:04:09.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叔叔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:10.76,0:04:11.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这该不会是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:12.19,0:04:14.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 只是蜡笔而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:14.59,0:04:15.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讨厌
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:16.45,0:04:17.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,连这里也有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:47.00,0:04:49.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,水中纪念碑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:49.70,0:04:50.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是怎么回事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:51.45,0:04:52.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好可怕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:52.41,0:04:53.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿真
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:56.17,0:04:57.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,水里面有一只钥匙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:02.44,0:05:03.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿真
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:04.42,0:05:05.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿真
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:07.25,0:05:08.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿真
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:11.42,0:05:12.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿真
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:13.74,0:05:14.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿真
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:15.18,0:05:16.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出什么事了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:21.04,0:05:24.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿真 振作一点 阿真
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:25.11,0:05:28.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿真…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:31.96,0:05:34.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,切断左手的动脉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:35.72,0:05:37.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也没有其它的刀痕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:37.82,0:05:39.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快点叫救护车
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:39.60,0:05:41.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 已经太迟了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:41.30,0:05:42.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么可能
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:42.94,0:05:45.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了 叫城户来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:45.08,0:05:45.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,城户
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:45.90,0:05:48.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是住在楼下的医学系学生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:48.45,0:05:49.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他是阿真的朋友
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:49.83,0:05:52.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是你孙子已经…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:52.11,0:05:54.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管 快去叫啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:54.51,0:05:55.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去叫
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:00.81,0:06:03.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,城户先生…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:07.18,0:06:08.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,城户先生？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:10.08,0:06:10.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,城户先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:13.51,0:06:15.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,城户先生…好臭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:16.15,0:06:18.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来是喝醉酒了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:19.85,0:06:21.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这房间是怎么回事？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:29.41,0:06:30.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是谁啊？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:31.19,0:06:33.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,城户先生 阿真先生出事了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:33.23,0:06:34.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请马上跟我来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:58.84,0:07:00.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿真…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:06.22,0:07:09.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,死者是宗田真先生 二十二岁
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:09.99,0:07:13.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是城南大学工学院建筑系四年级
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:14.24,0:07:18.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,死因是割断手腕动脉出血过多而死
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:19.89,0:07:22.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从他死后颈部的僵硬程度来看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:22.85,0:07:25.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,差不多已经死了二、三个小时了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:25.69,0:07:31.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么说推定死亡时间是下午六点到七点左右
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:31.55,0:07:32.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,警官
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:32.56,0:07:34.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是自杀不会错
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:34.61,0:07:36.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么？ 自杀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:37.35,0:07:38.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请到这里来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:40.18,0:07:40.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是这个
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:41.03,0:07:42.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是什么？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:42.61,0:07:45.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是阿真先生制造的建筑模型
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:46.18,0:07:48.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,水池里面有条钥匙是吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:49.19,0:07:50.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是玄关的钥匙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:51.10,0:07:53.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且经过特殊制造
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:53.47,0:07:55.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不容易复制
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:56.59,0:07:57.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且备份钥匙呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:57.94,0:08:02.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光江婆婆跟管理员各有一条
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:02.95,0:08:04.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们到达的时候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:04.59,0:08:05.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玄关的锁呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:06.52,0:08:07.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是锁住的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:07.69,0:08:08.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是说这间房间
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:08.87,0:08:10.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是个密室
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:10.95,0:08:12.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来如此
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:12.02,0:08:13.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以才判断是自杀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:13.97,0:08:15.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才没那回事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:16.27,0:08:17.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿真不会自杀的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:18.22,0:08:20.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我下午拿果汁过来的时候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:20.92,0:08:23.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他还说晚餐想吃南瓜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:24.50,0:08:26.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是几点钟呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:27.90,0:08:29.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,差不多是五点左右
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:30.09,0:08:32.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之后我就走了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:32.60,0:08:34.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想不到阿真就这样…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:35.10,0:08:36.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说的那个果汁是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:37.80,0:08:41.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我特制的 能止渴的果汁
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:42.08,0:08:45.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是一杯有蜂蜜蒜头香蕉的果汁
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:46.32,0:08:50.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之那时候一点异样都看不出来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:50.29,0:08:53.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且那孩子没有理由会自杀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:53.22,0:08:55.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿真他很烦恼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:57.24,0:08:58.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是什么意思？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:59.63,0:09:02.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他的毕业专题研究报告
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:02.44,0:09:03.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,进行得不是很顺利
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:04.34,0:09:05.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:06.50,0:09:09.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以他才会闷闷不乐吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:11.64,0:09:15.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有看到房间那些蜡笔乱画和这房间的布置
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:15.64,0:09:17.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我觉得他的心情很混乱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:18.09,0:09:19.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,警官
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:20.47,0:09:23.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这钥匙上面的白色东西是什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:24.87,0:09:26.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的 是什么呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:28.64,0:09:30.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你做什么啊 笨蛋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:31.17,0:09:33.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这该不会是卫生纸吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:33.74,0:09:35.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卫生纸？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:36.71,0:09:38.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果是纸巾或是其它的纸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:38.74,0:09:41.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算湿了也不会那么容易就溶解的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:42.37,0:09:44.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想大概是将卫生纸剪成条状
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:45.34,0:09:46.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后做成绳子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:47.67,0:09:52.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 钥匙上面为什么要弄这个东西呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:52.72,0:09:56.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个嘛 他的个性是有点奇怪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:56.72,0:09:58.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想大概是兴趣的问题吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:58.98,0:10:00.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之这间房间是密室…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:00.82,0:10:02.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是密室
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:02.36,0:10:02.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:03.55,0:10:04.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们看那里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:04.92,0:10:06.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,气窗是打开的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:07.74,0:10:08.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,白痴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:08.95,0:10:12.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么小的缝隙 你想人可以穿来穿去吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:14.72,0:10:18.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看 气窗的缝隙只有十五公分
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:20.30,0:10:22.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其它的窗户都被锁住了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:22.85,0:10:24.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以这是一间完整的密室
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:25.35,0:10:28.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过我还是觉得他不是自杀的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:29.47,0:10:33.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在黑漆漆的地方无法正确的割到动脉吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:33.20,0:10:34.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黑漆漆…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:34.83,0:10:38.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们进来的时候没有灯光吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:39.97,0:10:41.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过浴室就…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:41.71,0:10:43.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,里面也是没亮的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:44.16,0:10:46.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我开灯之后再进去的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:47.40,0:10:50.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在死亡推定时间的下午六点到七点左右
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:50.95,0:10:52.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,外面的天还没有黑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:52.65,0:10:55.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是浴室那里没有窗户
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:55.46,0:10:58.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在没有开灯之下要准确对准手腕是做不到的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:00.29,0:11:04.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也许是犯人在犯案后将灯给关掉了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:05.36,0:11:06.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果是他杀的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:07.11,0:11:09.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那墙壁这些蜡笔画应该就是犯人故意画上去的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:10.83,0:11:12.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在剩下钥匙了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:12.88,0:11:17.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,犯人是如何将钥匙放进水中的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:18.42,0:11:20.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有两个疑点
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:21.33,0:11:25.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么犯人将那条柱子和门把上 不像墙壁一样乱画
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:25.74,0:11:29.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而是整齐的一条线呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:30.85,0:11:31.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:32.71,0:11:33.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那气窗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:35.03,0:11:39.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很难想象犯人没有注意到那边早就被打开
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:40.79,0:11:41.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:42.27,0:11:44.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打开的不只是那个气窗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:44.57,0:11:45.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我明白了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:46.19,0:11:48.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我明白了 警官
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:49.63,0:11:50.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我收回前言 
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:50.94,0:11:53.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是一个他杀事件
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:54.64,0:11:56.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请大家跟我来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:57.81,0:12:00.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要解开这把戏的关键
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:01.16,0:12:03.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是这个信箱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:04.42,0:12:05.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,犯人首先
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:06.88,0:12:09.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,将一条线连接在模型上面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:09.82,0:12:11.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后拉到玄关那里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:11.65,0:12:13.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从信箱将线拉出来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:13.22,0:12:15.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后用钥匙上锁
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:16.27,0:12:19.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再将钥匙放入一边的线
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:19.43,0:12:21.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,将另外一条线慢慢拉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:21.83,0:12:23.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,钥匙就会慢慢往房间方向过去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:24.33,0:12:26.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,掉到模型的水中的时候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:26.74,0:12:28.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卫生纸遇水就断了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:28.63,0:12:30.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就掉到水里了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:33.02,0:12:34.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如何？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:35.39,0:12:37.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样谜底就解开了吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:38.25,0:12:40.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来如此 不愧是毛利
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:43.72,0:12:45.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来是这样 所以才会…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:46.23,0:12:48.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叔叔 我有点不太明白
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:49.31,0:12:51.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个玄关到客厅
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:51.19,0:12:53.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是个直角方向吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:54.08,0:12:55.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那又如何
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:55.70,0:12:58.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果是从这里把线拉到客厅的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:58.41,0:13:02.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,应该会在那条柱子上面留下痕迹的啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:07.66,0:13:09.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没…没有痕迹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:10.15,0:13:13.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,犯人故意在柱子上面涂上蜡笔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:13.72,0:13:16.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是为了让人知道他不是利用线去作案的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:18.31,0:13:19.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且这里也有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:20.07,0:13:21.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了 我明白了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:22.13,0:13:26.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,犯人是直接从信箱将大门的锁给…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:27.16,0:13:29.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也不是这样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:33.24,0:13:35.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了 气窗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:35.86,0:13:37.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才那种手法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:37.44,0:13:40.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,犯人是利用气窗来完成的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:42.33,0:13:45.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看起来是有可能...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:45.16,0:13:47.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 那是不可能的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:49.55,0:13:52.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们看 那里有一只狗吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:53.10,0:13:54.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它是只很尽责的看门狗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:55.15,0:13:57.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,除了家人之外 看到其它人都会叫
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:58.73,0:13:59.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对吧 城户
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:00.91,0:14:02.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我常常被它吠
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:03.29,0:14:06.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,庭院那里一片空旷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:06.21,0:14:08.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果有人在那里做奇怪动作的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:08.81,0:14:10.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它会吠的更大声
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:10.61,0:14:11.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很麻烦的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:12.49,0:14:14.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那这样也不行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:15.78,0:14:18.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来果然是自杀 警官
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:20.62,0:14:22.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 他是被杀的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:23.46,0:14:24.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且犯人是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:28.08,0:14:29.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被害者的伤口只有一个地方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:30.37,0:14:31.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一点其它伤痕也没有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:31.92,0:14:33.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一刀就狠狠地割了下去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:34.72,0:14:36.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能够这么准确做到的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:36.37,0:14:38.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有医学观念的人才做得到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:39.50,0:14:42.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是到底是利用什么方法呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:46.48,0:14:47.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,路灯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:48.65,0:14:49.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:49.96,0:14:51.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玄关那边的上衣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:52.10,0:14:53.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,整个房间都是蜡笔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:53.96,0:14:54.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:55.22,0:14:55.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来如此
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:56.57,0:14:58.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以才会将那个窗户稍微打开
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:58.83,0:15:00.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,形成一个似是而非的密室
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:07.51,0:15:08.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在只剩下证据了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:09.40,0:15:11.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定有什么线索
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:11.76,0:15:12.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:14.40,0:15:14.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:16.10,0:15:17.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个味道…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:21.12,0:15:22.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是从这里传出来的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:23.29,0:15:24.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说不定...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:28.87,0:15:29.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:31.27,0:15:32.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老婆婆
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:33.58,0:15:36.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是老婆婆装果汁的杯子吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:38.23,0:15:39.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:39.40,0:15:42.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真稀奇 阿真竟然会洗杯子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:43.02,0:15:43.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:44.48,0:15:46.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样证据就有了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:47.07,0:15:49.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你的协助
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:49.56,0:15:50.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天就到此…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:51.02,0:15:52.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:53.38,0:15:56.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道犯人是用什么方法了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:56.57,0:15:58.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么 真的吗？ 柯南
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:59.81,0:16:01.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我现在做给你们看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:01.35,0:16:03.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老婆婆 钥匙借我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:03.24,0:16:05.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋 你怎么可能会知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:06.58,0:16:09.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小朋友 钥匙就行了吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:09.80,0:16:10.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拿去吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:10.50,0:16:11.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:11.69,0:16:12.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们在这里等一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:24.92,0:16:26.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你到底想做什么？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:27.14,0:16:28.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别问这么多了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:28.86,0:16:30.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 老婆婆
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:30.92,0:16:32.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等我出去之后将灯给关掉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:32.68,0:16:35.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就跟我们第一次进来的时候一样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:35.69,0:16:36.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:36.86,0:16:37.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:38.01,0:16:40.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要开始了 大家要安静喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:42.26,0:16:43.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神气什么啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:51.96,0:16:53.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像有东西掉下来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:02.38,0:17:03.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,甲虫
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:04.23,0:17:05.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是雄性甲虫
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:32.93,0:17:34.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:15.19,0:18:16.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是路灯啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:19.34,0:18:20.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么样？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:20.72,0:18:21.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,柯南
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:23.00,0:18:23.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来如此
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:24.31,0:18:26.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是犯人使用的手法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:26.96,0:18:29.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是你为什么用甲虫呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:29.18,0:18:30.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是味道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:31.27,0:18:33.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就在这纪念品的塔顶上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:33.20,0:18:35.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沾有雌性甲虫的味道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:36.31,0:18:37.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:37.35,0:18:39.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,铺在玄关那边的上衣是？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:39.86,0:18:42.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是为了让甲虫方便行走
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:42.28,0:18:43.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,犯人特地放的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:44.72,0:18:46.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为平地或是光滑的地方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:46.44,0:18:48.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,甲虫就很难移动了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:49.03,0:18:51.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里的走廊和客厅都铺着地毯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:53.85,0:18:56.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是说 这里的环境有利于犯人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:56.97,0:18:58.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,柯南 你真厉害
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:59.77,0:19:01.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是刚才的甲虫
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:01.34,0:19:02.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是从哪里拿来的？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:03.27,0:19:06.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我擅自将城户先生家里面养的甲虫给拿来用
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:07.29,0:19:10.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跑掉了一只 对不起 城户先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:11.37,0:19:12.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 没关系
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:13.60,0:19:14.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,城户先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:14.53,0:19:17.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今晚我去叫你之前 你进过这个房间吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:18.64,0:19:20.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 没进来过
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:20.77,0:19:21.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:22.24,0:19:23.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会错吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:24.13,0:19:26.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然 你为什么这样问
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:27.05,0:19:29.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么为什么城户先生的手帕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:29.56,0:19:32.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会有老婆婆特制的果汁的味道呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:35.24,0:19:37.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老婆婆拿果汁过来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:37.66,0:19:39.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是晚上五点左右
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:41.45,0:19:42.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,城户先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:42.81,0:19:46.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你把阿真先生他喝过的杯子洗过了吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:46.95,0:19:47.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且在那时候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:48.36,0:19:51.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你用自己的手帕将滴在地上的果汁给擦掉了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:53.02,0:19:55.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你之所以会这么做
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:55.53,0:19:56.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是因为…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:57.49,0:19:58.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雄性甲虫
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:58.95,0:20:00.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比起雌性甲虫的味道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:00.40,0:20:02.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它反而会被果汁强烈的味道给吸引过去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:02.67,0:20:05.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跑到纪念品以外的地方去就麻烦了 对吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:08.78,0:20:13.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是将雌性的甲虫体液擦在这纪念品的塔顶吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:14.55,0:20:15.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,城户
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:15.81,0:20:17.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道真的是你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:23.07,0:20:24.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请把手帕拿出来吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:26.73,0:20:28.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我真是糊涂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:28.86,0:20:30.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,布了这个局把他杀了之后
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:30.58,0:20:32.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就得意忘形
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:33.15,0:20:35.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就忘记把手帕处理掉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:35.95,0:20:38.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大喝庆功酒睡着了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:38.73,0:20:40.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你为什么要杀害阿真先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:41.30,0:20:42.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在一年前
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:43.02,0:20:47.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是他提议从大学医院将安眠药给偷出来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:47.65,0:20:48.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后卖出去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:49.38,0:20:50.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,结果现在他却说…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:51.09,0:20:53.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们还是住手吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:54.42,0:20:56.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我听说今晚你会过来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:56.71,0:20:58.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果他泄漏了出来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:58.71,0:21:00.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,后果可不堪设想
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:00.51,0:21:01.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这家伙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:07.94,0:21:09.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想阿真他…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:10.16,0:21:12.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的是后悔了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:13.15,0:21:14.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以才会不想再继续下去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:16.19,0:21:18.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然现在讲这些已经太迟了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:19.30,0:21:20.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其实人的生命
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:21.23,0:21:23.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比你想象中的还要宝贵啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:26.14,0:21:27.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这一点
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:27.88,0:21:29.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就在监狱里面好好的反省吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:30.46,0:21:34.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,花上你的大半人生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:07.67,0:23:09.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光江婆婆真可怜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:10.98,0:23:12.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然不能代替阿真
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:14.03,0:23:16.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们有空就过去看看她吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:18.58,0:23:21.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过今晚的柯南真厉害
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:21.65,0:23:23.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让我非常惊讶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:23.62,0:23:24.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:24.49,0:23:27.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为平时都在叔叔旁边听着他那些名推理
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:28.18,0:23:31.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是所谓的「耳濡目染」
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:31.95,0:23:33.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,托我的福
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:33.55,0:23:37.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让你在不知不觉中学会如何做一个出色的侦探
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:39.21,0:23:43.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叔叔最好多多学习怎么做一个出色的侦探
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:49.45,0:23:51.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,逮捕真凶？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:51.30,0:23:54.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快找 快把高木和佐藤给找出来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:57.02,0:23:57.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,首先
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:57.89,0:23:59.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要调查东田先生在案发之前最后去过的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:00.08,0:24:02.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那间居酒屋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:02.36,0:24:03.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难…难道说
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:04.51,0:24:05.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道这个房间是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:06.27,0:24:08.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个人也住在这公寓里面吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:09.86,0:24:10.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Next Conan
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:11.16,0:24:14.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本厅刑事恋爱物语2(前篇)
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:15.89,0:24:18.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Next Conan's HINT
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:18.25,0:24:19.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿笠博士的新发明
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:20.25,0:24:21.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下一回是恋爱物语2
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:21.91,0:24:23.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是佐藤警官和我的恋爱物语吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:23.48,0:24:25.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果是这样 我一定横刀夺爱
